file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Sample App
  version: 0.0.1
paths:
  /item:
    get:
      operationId: itemGet
      responses:
        200:
          description: ok
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Item'
    options:
      operationId: itemOptions
      responses:
        200:
          description: ok
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
components:
  schemas:
    Item:
      required:
      - name
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        related:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Item'
